articles.description: Trae Young's spirits were buoyed by a surprise phone call Wednesday from Hall of Famer Oscar Robertson, who gave the Sooners freshman "some good advice."
articles.headline: Trae Young gets 'good advice' from Hall of Famer Oscar Robertson

images.caption: Trae Young is ice cold from the field, shooting 4-of-16 and scoring 19 points, as the No. 7 Red Raiders defeat the No. 23 Sooners 88-78.
images.name: Oklahoma falls to Texas Tech, suffers fourth consecutive loss

articles.description: Commodores senior Riley LaChance joins The Paul Finebaum Show to recap his game-winning shot vs. MSU and share his outlook on the rest of the season.
articles.headline: LaChance hopes Vandy can make late-season run

images.caption: Commodores senior Riley LaChance joins The Paul Finebaum Show to recap his game-winning shot vs. MSU and share his outlook on the rest of the season.
images.name: LaChance hopes Vandy can make late-season run

articles.description: Clemson junior guard Shelton Mitchell is out of the hospital but remains in the concussion protocol following an injury suffered during Wednesday's loss to Florida State.
articles.headline: Clemson's Shelton Mitchell exits hospital after hit to head

articles.description: Mark Schlabach joins OTL to discuss a U.S. District Court denying a motion to dismiss federal criminal charges against three of the 10 men arrested for their alleged roles in the FBI's two-year investigation into college basketball corruption.
articles.headline: Court denies dismissal off CBB probe

articles.description: Reggie Lynch maintains his innocence against sexual misconduct allegations but has dropped appeals of his Minnesota expulsion because he does not feel he could receive a fair hearing.
articles.headline: Reggie Lynch drops appeals of sexual misconduct rulings, accepts expulsion

articles.description: A U.S. District Court judge denied a motion Thursday to dismiss federal criminal charges against former Adidas executives James Gatto and Merl Code and former sports agent Christian Dawkins in the FBI's investigation into college basketball corruption.
articles.headline: Judge denies motion to drop charges in corruption case against ex-Adidas execs, agent

videos.description: Trae Young gets Oklahoma out in front early with a deep 3-pointer against TCU.
videos.headline: Young launches deep 3 for Sooners

videos.description: TCU's Ahmed Hamdy-Mohamed backs down a defender for a hook shot to finish a 10-0 run for the Horned Frogs.
videos.headline: Hamdy-Mohamed knocks down hook shot to cap 10-point run

videos.description: Trae Young finds Kameron McGusty in transition who converts the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: OU's McGusty goes up strong for and-1

videos.description: Trae Young gets the Sooners back out in front with a 3 quickly followed by a technical foul for TCU head coach Jamie Dixon.
videos.headline: Young hits 3, TCU coach gets tech

videos.description: Trae Young shows off his range by hitting a 3-pointer from the TCU logo.
videos.headline: Young pulls up from logo for 3

videos.description: Oklahoma's Rashard Odomes cuts to the hoop and extends for the basket, drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Odomes leaps and reaches for hoop

videos.description: Desmond Bane gets out in front on the fastbreak for a big dunk.
videos.headline: Bane hammers dunk for TCU

videos.description: Jamuni McNeace elevates for a huge dunk off a pass from Trae Young.
videos.headline: McNeace throws down for Oklahoma

videos.description: Trae Young crosses over and pulls up from deep to keep Oklahoma close to TCU.
videos.headline: Young pulls up for fifth 3-pointer

videos.description: Trae Young fires a bounce pass to Kameron McGusty, who gets the bucket on basket interference by TCU.
videos.headline: Young threads needle on pass to McGusty

videos.description: Trae Young finds Kameron McGusty in transition who pulls up for a 3 to tie the game at 83.
videos.headline: McGusty ties it with corner 3

videos.description: Kameron McGusty gets open off an offensive rebound to hit a clutch 3 to put Oklahoma up 88-87.
videos.headline: McGusty's late 3 gives OU lead

videos.description: Trae Young goes for 39 points and 14 assists as Oklahoma becomes the 3rd team to win two road games vs. AP top-10 teams before January ('76-77 Notre Dame and '61-62 Ohio State).
videos.headline: Young drops 39 as Oklahoma beats TCU

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Young drops 39 as Oklahoma beats TCU) 2017/12/30 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trae Young explains how he stays focused with lofty ambitions on him while playing for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Young: 'I came here to win a championship'

videos.description: Oklahoma freshman Trae Young nets a historic 39 points and 14 assists to lead the Sooners to a comeback win over TCU.
videos.headline: Historic effort by Young in comeback win
